N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 402.1 - Definitions

State Regulations
(a) Personal
property shall mean tangible property of all types other than real property, and shall include any right, title or interest in or to such tangible
property. (b) Real estate shall
mean real property or any right, title or interest in or to real property, and
shall include easements of all types. Notes
